I am a Berlin-based junior full-stack web developer in search of a new challenge and I would
love the opportunityto join your company. My experience is mainly with React, Redux,
Javascript, HTML, Node.js and Express but I also have experience working with Vue.js,
MongoDB, Postgresql and Git. At present I am dedicating my energies to furthering my skills
with Typescript, exploring the full potential of CSS and improving my knowledge of the
MERN stack. In October 2020 I finished an intensive full stack web development bootcamp
focused on Javascript and since then have been working on several personal projects,
building onmy stack and exploring new technologies.
I started learning web development through the self-taught route from the beginning of
2020, and cemented my knowledge in an intensive full-time web development bootcamp.
The bootcamp not only provided a well structured environment for learning but ensured that
I was completely focused on the most current and relevant technologies. Our experienced
and dedicated tutors gave us a firm grounding in industry standards and expectations, i.e.
data protection, overcoming browser compatibility issues, effective testing practices and the
prevention of malicious attacks.
Since finishing my education, I have been working daily on furthering my own learning and
strengthening my portfolio. Amongst my deployed projects are three responsive React.js
applications. These include: an e-commerce site (which features integrated payment
methods), a social network site which uses sockets.io (showing online users and instant
messaging) and a geocaching site which uses address to coordinates technology from the
mapbox api. Feel free to take a look at my github for a full rundown of my other completed
works.
At this stage in my career, my main goal is to learn as much as possible through hands-on
experience and really grow my skill-set as a developer. I value working and learning as part
of a team and pride myself on being open, communicative and easy to work with. I feel
working with a company which prides itself on being modern and goal-driven could be an
environment that I would be happy to grow in, so if you think there are any other positions
or internships related to my skillset that I would also be suited for, I would be delighted with
the opportunity. I believe I bring the enthusiasm and dedication of a junior web developer,
and the up-to-date skillset for today’s web development tasks. I am fully able to work onsite
in Berlin or remote, and am available for an immediate start.
Dear InVision team,
